summary: An Ordinance accepting a deed from L. J. Sprengle and Jennie G. Sprengle, his wife, to the City of Seattle, dated the 29th day of August, 1905, to certain portions of Sections Twenty-one (21) in Township Twenty-five (25) North, of Range four (4) east of the Williamette Meridian in Capitol Hill Extension and addition to the City of Seattle.
